   PA Wire/PA Images / Sturgeon described Trump’s decision as “profoundly regrettable”. She said: “Climate change is one of the biggest challenges of our time. “The president of the USA’s decision to withdraw from the Paris Accord is profoundly regrettable.” PA Media 
